'''''Galactic Bandits''''' was a [[Holodrama/Legends|holodrama]] that [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] watched when he was a young boy. It featured wanted criminals from across the [[Galaxy/Legends|galaxy]]. One of the featured ones was [[Evet Scy'rrep]].

